//? Step 1.  go to Tailwindcss.com --> get started --> UsingPostCSS --> copy the install css package with "vite"
//! i.e    "npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite"

//? Step 2. add tailwind confug file 
//! npx tailwindcss init -p

//? Step 3. in package.json file add script
//!  i.e     ""scripts": {
//!               "script": "vite"
//!           }

//? in starting if you add "-y" then you dont need to add any script file 
//!   npx tailwindcss init -y

//? To Run the code 
//! npx run start


